  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to Improved national education policies and plans to advance access to equitable and quality Basic education with a lifelong learning perspective in Abuja region</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The SGD4 national consultations organized by Abuja office in the countries have noted that inequality in education remains a persistent challenge. Focus areas will be i) Empowering stakeholders in education to engage in a review of the right to education in national legislation; ii) Assisting governments in the assessment, formulation, monitoring and review of their education sector policies and plans, with an emphasis on the SDG4 target 4.2 relative to ECCE in the perspective of development of lifelong learning systems; iii) Promoting the creation of data-rich environments for decision-making in policy and planning and iv) advocating for the passing of the convention of non discrimination in education.</narrative>
  </description>
